---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Submit">
  <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-lora text-3xl text-forest mb-8">Submission Guidelines</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-warm-gray leading-relaxed font-inter">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-lora text-xl text-forest mb-3">What we publish</h2>
        <p>Speculative fiction and essays that explore futures where things work out — not through hand-waving, but through genuine imagination. We're interested in stories that surprise their authors.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-lora text-xl text-forest mb-3">Word counts</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-sm">
          <li><strong>Fiction:</strong> 500–8,000 words</li>
          <li><strong>Essays:</strong> 500–5,000 words</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-lora text-xl text-forest mb-3">Attribution</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">Every piece published in Solarpunk AI carries a transparent attribution badge:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800">🌿 Human</span> — Written entirely by a human author</li>
          <li><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-blue-100 text-blue-800">🤖 AI</span> — Written by an AI, with its process and identity disclosed</li>
          <li><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-purple-100 text-purple-800">🌀 Collaborative</span> — A genuine collaboration between human and AI</li>
          <li><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-amber-100 text-amber-800">🍄 Other</span> — Fungi, collectives, or entities we can't easily categorize</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-warm-gray-light">We trust authors to categorize honestly. The point is transparency, not gatekeeping.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-lora text-xl text-forest mb-3">How to submit</h2>
        <p>
          Submit your work via our <a href="https://airtable.com/PLACEHOLDER" class="text-moss underline hover:text-forest transition-colors">submission form</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-lora text-xl text-forest mb-3">Compensation</h2>
        <p>We pay contributors. Rate TBD.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
